an Hanák]]</s> || <s>Documentary</s> || <s>24</s> |- | <s>[[The Sun in a Net]] (1963)</s><ref name="Slovak film"/> || <s>[[Štefan Uher]]</s> || <s>Drama</s> || <s>24</s> |- | [[Starci na chmelu|Hop Pickers]] (1964) || [[Ladislav Rychman]] || Romantic Musical || 24 |- | [[The Ear]] (1970) || [[Karel Kachyňa]] || Thriller || 24 |- | [[The Joke (film)|The Joke]] (1968) || [[Jaromil Jireš]] || Drama || 24 |- ! rowspan="4"|11 | [[The Cassandra Cat]] (1963) || [[Vojtěch Jasný]] || Fantasy || 22 |- | [[Journey to the Beginning of Time]] (1955) || [[Karel Zeman]] || Adventure, Science Fiction || 22 |- | [[Witchhammer]] (1969) || [[Otakar Vávra]] || Historical || 22 |- | [[Capricious Summer]] (1968) || [[Jiří Menzel]] || Comedy || 22 |- ! 12 | [[The Fabulous World of Jules Verne]] (1954) || [[Karel Zeman]] || Adventure, Science Fiction || 21 |- ! rowspan="2"|13 | [[Erotikon (1929 film)|Erotikon]] (1929) || [[Gustav Machatý]] || Silent, Romantic || 20 |- | [[Larks on a String]] (1969) || [[Jiří Menzel]] || Drama || 20 |- ! rowspan="3"|14 | [[The Idiot Returns]] (1999) || [[Saša Gedeon]] || Romantic, Drama, Comedy || 19 |- | [[Nebeští jezdci|Sky Riders]] (1968) || [[Jindřich Polák]] || War || 19 |- | [[Oil Lamps (film)|Oil Lamps]] (1971) || [[Juraj Herz]] || Drama || 19 |- ! rowspan="3"|15 | [[The White Dove (1960 film)|The White Dove]] (1960) || [[František Vláčil]] || Drama || 18 |- | [[A Midsummer Night's Dream (1959 film)|A Midsummer Night's Dream]] (1959) || [[Jiří Trnka]] || Animation, Fantasy || 18 |- | [[Old Czech Legends]] (1953) || [[Jiří Trnka]] || Animation, Fantasy || 18 |- |colspan="5"|Source:<ref name="nostalghia2007">{{cite web|title=Filmové dědictví 2007|url=http://nostalghia.cz/pages/archiv/udalosti/2007/070406.php|website=Nostalghia.cz|accessdate=18 January 2017}}</ref> |}
