* {{cite book|title=Labyrinths of Reason: Paradox, Puzzles, and the Frailty of Knowledge|year=1988}}
* {{cite book|title=The Ultimate: The Great Armchair Debates Settled Once and for All|year=1990}}
* {{cite book|title=Prisoner's Dilemma: [[John von Neumann]], Game Theory, and the Puzzle of the Bomb|year=1992|isbn=978-0385415804}}
* {{cite book|title=Biggest Secrets: More Uncensored Truth About All Sorts of Stuff You Are Never Supposed to Know|year=1993}}
* {{cite book|title=Carl Sagan: A Life in the Cosmos|year=1999}}
